{"tid":579817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"訪問曾俊華片突下架","createTime":"2018-03-04T03:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T06:48:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1fb978dff501f27ff6ca5068450ee9dc35e5bc0f","tid":579817,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T03:15:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180304/20321619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180304%2F20321619&d=6mJNEbv3V4NV%2B0JsR8zBXxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=8f43bbe2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180304%2F20321619&h=c8325bbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180304/20321619</a><br />\n<br />\n訪問曾俊華片突下架<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180304/large/a0603a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180304%2Flarge%2Fa0603a.gif&h=ac31ce17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前財爺曾俊華早前為美國公關公司愛德曼拍片，但片段錯指他是正式財政司長。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】久未公開露面的前財政司司長曾俊華，早前為美國公關公司愛德曼（Edelman）拍片，分享贏取市民信任心得，直指上屆政府民望直墮谷底。片段原本在該公司香港分部facebook及YouTube網站發表，惟昨深夜卻神秘下架，引發揣測。愛德曼解釋，因製作人員打錯曾的職銜，片段會在修改後重新上載上網。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公關公司：打錯職銜<br />\n<br />\n根據YouTube版本的片段，曾俊華在英文訪問短片開首即指，「任何新政府班子履新都會有蜜月期，而上屆政府民望直墮谷底，如新政府上場後信任度未見回升，他會真的驚訝」。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華認為，政府要讓香港市民融入社會（to engage with people in Hong Kong），須用心傳遞（convey）他們的訊息。惟相關片段昨深夜卻全部低調下架，一度引發公眾揣測，片段因內容敏感「被審查」。<br />\n<br />\n據《明報》報道，曾俊華前晚曾將片段分享到個人fb專頁，隨即有網民留言指出，片中將其職銜，將前財政司司長寫成「Formal Financial Secretary（正式財政司司長）」。<br />\n本報在YouTube版片段下架前，亦發現曾俊華職銜有相關錯誤。愛德曼香港發言人稱，留意到片段內曾俊華職銜字眼有錯，故先行將片段下架，待完成修改後，會再次將片段上載上網。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭啟源"},{"pid":"fd9bd4d0a5b782bce1dde71c72412d6d79bd8590","tid":579817,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T03:15:59.000Z","msg":"死咗咁"},{"pid":"0ebe497d5e2232540902fa54ec8818847a88b6c2","tid":579817,"uid":91771,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T03:38:46.000Z","msg":"Former同formal...<br />\nAuto correct又出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3b89e437778bf7c5e961354a3b55772e3ccfe9","tid":579817,"uid":14009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ebe497d5e2232540902fa54ec8818847a88b6c2","tid":579817,"uid":91771,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T03:38:46.000Z","msg":"Former同formal...<br />\nAuto correct又出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T03:45:55.000Z","msg":"咁都錯又 kai d 既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f290a778c6060cbb913ede172e82255e251d2fb0","tid":579817,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:30:20.000Z","msg":"下架你條命"},{"pid":"2531abec9167fa9d2ada8d5db8953a4131fd7ed8","tid":579817,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:48:10.000Z","msg":"下架你條命"}]}